an utter beauty gawd , i hope this is n't a forgotten recording . this is oregon at their early best : unselfconsciousness ; innocence ; no formula , no regard for sales - just love of musical communication on the most intimate scale . they understood the value of silence and patience . and witchi-tai to alone is worth buying this recording for - it , like precious few recordings , brings tears to my eyes and makes me glad to be alive and have ears